description: Returns a list of ManagedNotificationChildEvents for a specified aggregate ManagedNotificationEvent, ordered by creation time in reverse chronological order (newest first).

parameters.name: aggregateManagedNotificationEventArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the ManagedNotificationEvent.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token. If a non-null pagination token is returned in a result, pass its value in another request to retrieve more entries.

nested_items.name: managedNotificationChildEvents
nested_items.description: A pagination token. If a non-null pagination token is returned in a result, pass its value in another request to retrieve more entries.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the ManagedNotificationChildEvent.

nested_items.name: managedNotificationConfigurationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the ManagedNotificationConfiguration.

nested_items.name: relatedAccount
nested_items.description: The account that related to the ManagedNotificationChildEvent.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The creation time of the ManagedNotificationChildEvent.

nested_items.name: childEvent
nested_items.description: The content of the ManagedNotificationChildEvent.

nested_items.name: schemaVersion
nested_items.description: The schema version of the ManagedNotificationChildEvent.

nested_items.name: sourceEventMetadata
nested_items.description: Contains all event metadata present identically across all NotificationEvents. All fields are present in Source Events via Eventbridge.

nested_items.name: eventOriginRegion
nested_items.description: The Region where the notification originated.

nested_items.name: source
nested_items.description: The source service of the notification.

nested_items.name: eventType
nested_items.description: The event Type of the notification.

nested_items.name: messageComponents
nested_items.description: Contains the headline message component.

nested_items.name: headline
nested_items.description: A sentence long summary. For example, titles or an email subject line.

nested_items.name: aggregationDetail
nested_items.description: Provides detailed information about the dimensions used for event summarization and aggregation.

nested_items.name: summarizationDimensions
nested_items.description: Properties used to summarize aggregated events.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the SummarizationDimensionDetail.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: Value of the property used to summarize aggregated events.

nested_items.name: eventStatus
nested_items.description: The perceived nature of the event.
Values:
HEALTHY.
All EventRules are ACTIVE and any call can be run.
UNHEALTHY.
Some EventRules are ACTIVE and some are INACTIVE. Any call can be run.

nested_items.name: notificationType
nested_items.description: The Type of the event causing this notification.
Values:
ALERT.
A notification about an event where something was triggered, initiated, reopened, deployed, or a threshold was breached.
WARNING.
A notification about an event where an issue is about to arise. For example, something is approaching a threshold.
ANNOUNCEMENT.
A notification about an important event. For example, a step in a workflow or escalation path or that a workflow was updated.
INFORMATIONAL.
A notification about informational messages. For example, recommendations, service announcements, or reminders.

nested_items.name: aggregateManagedNotificationEventArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the ManagedNotificationEvent that is associated with this ManagedNotificationChildEvent.

nested_items.name: organizationalUnitId
nested_items.description: The Organizational Unit Id that an AWS account belongs to.
